{
  "sn6.13:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6 ",
  "sn6.13:0.2": "2. Dutiyavagga ",
  "sn6.13:0.3": "13. Andhakavindasutta ",
  "sn6.13:1.1": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā māgadhesu viharati andhakavinde. ",
  "sn6.13:1.2": "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā rattandhakāratimisāyaṃ abbhokāse nisinno hoti, devo ca ekamekaṃ phusāyati. ",
  "sn6.13:1.3": "Atha kho brahmā sahampati abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ andhakavindaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. ",
  "sn6.13:1.4": "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho brahmā sahampati bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: ",
  "sn6.13:2.1": "“Sevetha pantāni senāsanāni, ",
  "sn6.13:2.2": "Careyya saṃyojanavippamokkhā; ",
  "sn6.13:2.3": "Sace ratiṃ nādhigaccheyya tattha, ",
  "sn6.13:2.4": "Saṃghe vase rakkhitatto satīmā. ",
  "sn6.13:3.1": "Kulākulaṃ piṇḍikāya caranto, ",
  "sn6.13:3.2": "Indriyagutto nipako satimā; ",
  "sn6.13:3.3": "Sevetha pantāni senāsanāni, ",
  "sn6.13:3.4": "Bhayā pamutto abhaye vimutto. ",
  "sn6.13:4.1": "Yattha bheravā sarīsapā, ",
  "sn6.13:4.2": "Vijju sañcarati thanayati devo; ",
  "sn6.13:4.3": "Andhakāratimisāya rattiyā, ",
  "sn6.13:4.4": "Nisīdi tattha bhikkhu vigatalomahaṃso. ",
  "sn6.13:5.1": "Idañhi jātu me diṭṭhaṃ, ",
  "sn6.13:5.2": "nayidaṃ itihītihaṃ; ",
  "sn6.13:5.3": "Ekasmiṃ brahmacariyasmiṃ, ",
  "sn6.13:5.4": "sahassaṃ maccuhāyinaṃ. ",
  "sn6.13:6.1": "Bhiyyo pañcasatā sekkhā, ",
  "sn6.13:6.2": "dasā ca dasadhā dasa; ",
  "sn6.13:6.3": "Sabbe sotasamāpannā, ",
  "sn6.13:6.4": "atiracchānagāmino. ",
  "sn6.13:7.1": "Athāyaṃ itarā pajā, ",
  "sn6.13:7.2": "puññabhāgāti me mano; ",
  "sn6.13:7.3": "Saṅkhātuṃ nopi sakkomi, ",
  "sn6.13:7.4": "musāvādassa ottapan”ti. "
}